.TH ZENPAD 1 "January 2026" "Zenpad 1.5.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
zenpad \- modern, lightweight text editor for Linux
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B zenpad
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fIFILE\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B Zenpad
is a modern, GTK-based text editor designed for efficiency and aesthetics.
It features syntax highlighting, multiple tabs, session restoration, and
tools designed for security professionals and Linux power users.
.PP
Zenpad supports over 100 programming languages with syntax highlighting,
Markdown preview, diff comparison, and analysis tools including hex viewer,
hash calculator, and various encoders/decoders.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Display version information and exit.
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
Display help message and exit.
.TP
\fB\-\-new\-window\fR
Open a new Zenpad window.
.TP
\fB\-\-preferences\fR
Open the preferences dialog.
.TP
\fB\-\-list\-encodings\fR
List all available file encodings.
